      "span_text": "Let ϑ denote the collection of all HMM parameters. [CITATION_1] showed that under the HMM dependency, the optimal test statistic is the local index of significance LISi = P ϑ (θi = 0|x x x), which can be computed using a fast forward-backward algorithm.",
